Package Application.Models

Class CustomerTable

java.lang.Object
Application.Models.Customer
Application.Models.CustomerTable
public class CustomerTable extends Customer
The CustomerTable Model meant to represent and store the actual displayed records in the MainMenuView Customer Table inherits and extends Customer functionality invalid input: '&' fields with the addition of the country name and state/province name required for display.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Michael Short

      public CustomerTable(Customer customer, String country, String stateProvince)
      This Constructor is used specifically when the Customer type object is already generated and needs to be converted to an CustomerTable with the additional country name and state/province name field info.
      Parameters:
      customer - The pre-generated customer
      country - The attached country name associated with the customer
      stateProvince - The attached state/province name associated with the customer
